snippet.title: Ybor Gold Amber Lager Review and Tampa Death Metal Bands
snippet.description:
I'm actually trying a beer for the first time, with you! It's the Ybor Gold Amber Lager from Florida Beer Company.

Florida Beer Co. Website:
https://www.floridabeer.com/

I'm also talking about the birth of death metal bands from Tampa, FL, which is where Ybor Gold was originally brewed.

I'll link to each band's channel below:

Obituary:
https://www.youtube.com/user/ObituaryTheBand

Morbid Angel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUDMrCf1SbVEIt4Ee6TE-2w

Deicide (video on the Earache Records channel):
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IJkMrl4AG8w

Iced Earth:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_-B-_fqZ02JdIyXJ04CBaQ

Please gives this video and thumbs up and make sure you're subscribed!

🍺  Follow Metal & Beer on Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/metalandbeer/

🎧  LISTEN to My Metal Music here:
https://www.jasonstallworth.com/music/
